Reference counting for nodes in VPN and ENCAP import route tables

VPN Node references to count:
    BIs
    vpn monitors

Encap Node references to count:
    BIs
    encap monitors


(lock => increment; unlock = decr and delete if 0)

route_node_match	longest match, incr upon success
route_node_lookup	exact match, incr upon success
route_node_get		exact match or create, incr always
route_top		get top node, incr upon success

see also TBDs in .c files



Count these references:

VPN import table:
    Node's BIs
    Node's VPN monitors

ENCAP import table
    Node's BIs
    Node's ENCAP monitors




